# Image Processing API

## Description

A RESTful API built with **Express** and **TypeScript** that processes images using the **Sharp** library. It accepts image filenames and optional dimensions as query parameters, resizes the image accordingly, and returns the result. This project is part of the Udacity Full-Stack Web Developer Nanodegree program.

## Setup

Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

Or to replicate from scratch:

```bash
npm init -y
npm i \
    cors express helmet sharp typescript
npm i -D \
    @eslint/js @types/cors @types/eslint @types/express \
    @types/helmet @types/jasmine @types/node @types/nodemon @types/sharp \
    @types/supertest eslint eslint-config-prettier eslint-plugin-prettier \
    globals jasmine jasmine-spec-reporter nodemon prettier supertest ts-node \
    typescript-eslint
```

